00:01:16.286 --> 00:01:17.546 A:middle
Now with this Mac App Store

00:01:17.546 --> 00:01:19.846 A:middle
redesign, we've added support

00:01:19.846 --> 00:01:22.126 A:middle
for a few new features including

00:01:22.126 --> 00:01:24.766 A:middle
app subtitles and app previews.

00:01:25.436 --> 00:01:26.446 A:middle
