00:01:26.446 --> 00:01:28.126 A:middle
features by signing into App

00:01:28.126 --> 00:01:30.246 A:middle
Store Connect or by using the

00:01:30.246 --> 00:01:31.856 A:middle
XML feed if you use that for

00:01:31.856 --> 00:01:32.756 A:middle
